{"tid":247202,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國資助20億　杜特蒂：意外之財","createTime":"2017-05-17T15:15:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-18T11:25:21.000Z","uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2b9b9c8f66c32394b6089afcc679f7af36b8953e","tid":247202,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T15:15:51.000Z","msg":"「一帶一路高峰論壇」前天落幕，但中國仍刻意拉攏周邊國家，不但與到訪的菲律賓總統杜特蒂簽屬協議，承諾加快對菲基礎建設高達約20億元台幣的資助計劃，並獲得菲國對共同開發南海資源持開放態度。中國國家主席習近平昨也會晤日本自民黨幹事長二階俊博，盼改善雙邊關係。<br />\n<br />\n從北京返抵菲律賓的杜特蒂（Rodrigo Duterte）昨舉行記者會，聲稱此行為菲國爭取到一筆「意外之財」，不但與習近平會面，且雙方簽訂多項協議，包括由中方提供近20億元台幣，資助菲國基建項目作的可行性研究，以及由中方為菲國興建戒毒康復中心等。<br />\n<br />\n對於國際法庭去年做出的南海仲裁案結果，杜特蒂稱無計劃以此「向中施壓」，對與中國和越南共同探勘南海的提議表示：「何樂而不為」，惟強調相關協議須「公平且平衡」。<br />\n<br />\n此外，習近平昨與日本自民黨幹事長二階俊博會面時，表達願改善雙邊關係的意願，習特別指「中日應本著以史為鑒精神，改善兩國關係」，並強調「兩國友好合作，是唯一的正確選擇」。<br />\n<br />\n至於因部署薩德系統問題而關係惡化的南韓，中國也趁舉辦峰會之際，由習近平、中國前外交國務委員唐家璇以及國務委員楊潔篪陸續接見南韓代表，表達願與新總統文在寅溝通的明確態度。（大陸中心╱綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://n2.hk/d/attachments/day_170517/20170517_5c3d9eb9d33365da017ciZvFcWlpGihC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn2.hk%2Fd%2Fattachments%2Fday_170517%2F20170517_5c3d9eb9d33365da017ciZvFcWlpGihC.jpg&h=7144a623&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://n2.hk/d/attachments/day_170517/20170517_0e26f0dd80828658afccFSw2HBCvlboC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn2.hk%2Fd%2Fattachments%2Fday_170517%2F20170517_0e26f0dd80828658afccFSw2HBCvlboC.jpg&h=cc67d9b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新聞來源連結:<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20170517/1120039\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Finternational%2F20170517%2F1120039&d=uw8R2zILh4IVFJjxqgttXEbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=8abcc537\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20170517/1120039</a>"},{"pid":"72ce7594b4f151002242fd47465633beb14e8d2e","tid":247202,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T15:27:26.000Z","msg":"樂觀SIR，你點睇而家個市呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce40328d657d19e101dee93233eef2fdb66ccb00","tid":247202,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T15:31:43.000Z","msg":"棋王要俾買路錢寨主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪賓仔一玩野條海上絲綢之路未出門口就先玩完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07353bc14bb5eeb9ac9e56f8466ed9d18ba8a64e","tid":247202,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T15:34:51.000Z","msg":"中共呢個政權真係好勁<br />\n<br />\n比錢外國, 就幾十億, 幾百億咁比<br />\n但自己國民 需要錢, 就一蚊都唔會比"},{"pid":"9bc268b66584b61a8735af4703826a6aa17388a8","tid":247202,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T15:46:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中共呢個政權真係好勁<br />\n<br />\n比錢外國, 就幾十億, 幾百億咁比<br />\n但自己國民 需要錢, 就一蚊都唔會比</blockquote><br />\n唔俾錢賓仔，蕉都無得你班人食呀"},{"pid":"37f49a2187365b1dbc80ed182a7f324efb03dc08","tid":247202,"uid":70505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T11:25:21.000Z","msg":"心諗，成二十億橫財<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 分分鐘重貪過中國"}]}